Welcome to the new CoderYouth

A code community for teenagers by teenagers

What is CoderYouth?

CoderYouth is a code community for teenagers by teenagers. Yes, there are already great communities out there, but having no adults makes us different. Our community is entirely formed by teenagers. Yes, even the organization. In CoderYouth, you can connect with like-minded people who understand you better than anyone else.

Who is CoderYouth for?

Any teenager between 13 and 20 years old attracted by technology. You don't need to have great projects or even know how to code! The only think that we'll ask you for is passion.

The CoderYouth Family

CoderYouth Chat

Communicate with the community. Share your work and get feedback, ask for help or have fun with loads of geeky puns.

CoderYouth Stories

Learn about the stories of other members, their projects more in a short interview format.

CoderYouth Mob

Community-based promoting. You've built an awesome thing, now let's get the world to know about it!

CoderYouth Talk

Monthly online meetings where you can showcase your work and get to know other members better.
